@node REQUIREMENTS "What do I need?"
@{b}REQUIREMENTS
============@{ub}

 * Kickstart 3.1.

 * AmigaOS 3.5.

 * 68020 or better processor.

 * 640x400 display (800x600 preferred).

 * 6 Meg RAM (2 Chip, 4 Fast).

@endnode


@node INSTALLATION "How do I install Sim4004?"
Installation is simple. It is performed using Installer v44 by Amiga Inc.
Simply extract the archive to a temporary directory and then double-click
the "Install 4004" icon. Follow the prompts until the install is complete.

A full installation performs the following tasks:
    * Required directory structure is created in the desired directory.
    * All files are copied to the appropriate locations.
    * A default preferences file is also copied.
    * An Environment variable (SIM4004_PREFS) is created that is meant
      to always point to the current preferences file.
    * The SIM4004: assign is set to point to the Sim4004 parent directory
      and added to s:user-startup.

That's it. You are now ready to use the application.
@endnode

