@node BUGS    "Bugs! What bugs?"

@{b}BUG LIST AS AT 09-October-2003
==============================@{ub}

 * Multiple Menu Selection does not work properly for Registers Window option.

@{b}BUGS FIXED IN Sim4004 v1.01
===========================@{ub}

 * ARexx documentation stated that HELP, CMDSHELL, RX and DOSCMD ARexx
   functions were not supported. This was not correct. They have always been
   supported. Documentation updated.
  
 * The lights.c example code calls the REMHARDWARE ARexx command on the ROM
   port when it should have been calling REMHARDWARE for the RAM port. Fixed.
  
 * The timer.c example code defines the parameters received by ARexx commands
   incorrectly. Fixed.
 
 * Sim4004 and cSim4004 did not send an ARexx message to the corresponding
   ARexx message port when the WRR instruction was executed. Fixed.
 
 * The i4002 RAM Editor window did not display correctly if the window was not
   positioned right over to the left of screen. This became worse the further
   you move away from the left of the screen. This is now fixed.

@endnode


